<!--
  com.decifer.handoff-publisher.plist
  Classification: DEPRECATED — do not install

  *** THIS PLIST IS SUPERSEDED AND MUST NOT BE INSTALLED ***

  handoff_publisher.py has been deleted. The intelligence pipeline now owns
  the full publish cycle including manifest and universe promotion.

  Replacement: ops/launchd/com.decifer.intelligence-pipeline.plist
  Replacement worker: run_intelligence_pipeline.py

  The replacement pipeline:
    - Runs once per trading day (pre-open, 16:45 Dubai / 12:45 UTC)
    - Writes data/live/active_opportunity_universe.json
    - Writes data/live/current_manifest.json with session-valid expiry (22:00 UTC)
    - The live bot reads the manifest every scan cycle — no periodic publisher needed

