    The 10-minute publisher with 15-minute TTL expired the manifest before or
    shortly after market open, causing the bot to fail closed for new entries
    even though the once-daily universe was still valid for the session.
    The correct model is: one pipeline run per day, session-valid manifest.

  If this file exists in ~/Library/LaunchAgents/, unload and remove it:
    launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.decifer.handoff-publisher.plist
    rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.decifer.handoff-publisher.plist
-->
